Most things are priced. Some things are make an offer. Feel free to haggle with the set prices.

I accept paypal (HIGHLY PREFERRED), money orders, and concealed cash (at your own risk). If you do use paypal, it would be great if you could cover the 50 cent fee but I know I can't charge it! I am in Canada, so shipping on a lot of things will be more than you might be used to (But I dont rip you off!). Usually 3$ on shirts (3$ US if your in the US, 3$ CDN if your in Canada), and 5-6-7$ (Again, whatever currency [US AND CANADA ONLY] you normally use) on pants or heavy items. I do not purchase insurance unless you ask for it and pay for it. I will do trades for things that I'm looking for.
